# Commit Message Template for GitHub Copilot

# Type: feat|fix|docs|style|refactor|test|chore
# Scope: component affected (optional)
# Description: brief description

# Example:
# feat(video-player): add AI generation controls
# fix(security): resolve XSS vulnerability in auth
# docs(readme): update deployment instructions

# Guidelines:
# - Use present tense ("add" not "added")
# - Keep first line under 72 characters
# - Reference issues/PRs when applicable
# - Include breaking changes in footer

# Breaking Changes:
# BREAKING CHANGE: describe what changed

# Closes: #123